{"version":0.1,"twitch_info":{"video_id":"2678666184","title":"LunarMagic","description":null,"chapters":[{"id":"","startMilliseconds":0,"lengthMilliseconds":9779000,"type":"GAME_CHANGE","description":"I Wanna Be the Guy","subDescription":"","thumbnailUrl":null,"gameId":"20716","gameDisplayName":"I Wanna Be the Guy","gameBoxArtUrl":"https://static-cdn.jtvnw.net/ttv-boxart/20716_IGDB-40x53.jpg"}],"streamer":{"name":"SerYoGa7","login":"seryoga7","id":39309540}},"embedded_data":{"twitch_badges":{}},"messages":[{"content_offset_seconds":551,"commenter":{"_id":"1372142368","display_name":"horrorstory_365","name":"horrorstory_365"},"message":{"body":"О, привет! Уже на Лунармэджик? Оперативно ты","user_color":null,"user_badges":[{"_id":"no_audio","version":"1"}]}},{"content_offset_seconds":621,"commenter":{"_id":"1372142368","display_name":"horrorstory_365","name":"horrorstory_365"},"message":{"body":"Ладно, просто снова поздравлю тебя с взятием пятого секрета. Ну, и удачи на Лунаре. Она будет определённо попроще.","user_color":null,"user_badges":[{"_id":"no_audio","version":"1"}]}},{"content_offset_seconds":706,"commenter":{"_id":"1372142368","display_name":"horrorstory_365","name":"horrorstory_365"},"message":{"body":"Это один из лучших боссов имхо. Из-за музыки по большей части. Одна из лучших в игре","user_color":null,"user_badges":[{"_id":"no_audio","version":"1"}]}},{"content_offset_seconds":772,"commenter":{"_id":"1372142368","display_name":"horrorstory_365","name":"horrorstory_365"},"message":{"body":"А вот на Кибере тебе придётся хорошенько помучиться... Будь готов, на нём очень многие встревают надолго, даже спидранеры.","user_color":null,"user_badges":[{"_id":"no_audio","version":"1"}]}},{"content_offset_seconds":777,"commenter":{"_id":"88101775","display_name":"deadema0","name":"deadema0"},"message":{"body":"deadema0 watched 20 consecutive streams and sparked a watch streak! ","user_color":"#0000FF","user_badges":[{"_id":"moderator","version":"1"}]}},{"content_